net.cloud.server.nio.packet.packets

Class LoginPacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.server.nio.packet.ReceiveOnlyPacket
      • net.cloud.server.nio.packet.packets.LoginPacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Packet

    public class LoginPacket
extends ReceiveOnlyPacket
    Deals with the login process. Receives username and password from the client. Then validates the login information, before responding back to the client.

      static class  LoginPacket.LoginResponsePacket
      A packet which the server sends as a response to the LoginPacket (a response to a client's request to login)

        public Packet decode(io.netty.buffer.ByteBuf data)
              throws BufferableException
        Description copied from interface: Packet
        Decodes the Packet. Takes the data and creates a copy of the specific Packet implementing class. The Packet returned is a copy with the members set according to the data, not the original.
        Parameters:
        data - The data required for the Packet, assumed to be without header.
        Returns:
        A copy of the Packet deserialized to reflect the provided data
        Throws:
        BufferableException - If there is an issue decoding a Bufferable object
